Package org.apache.commons.imaging.formats.tiff.constants

Class TiffConstants

java.lang.Object
org.apache.commons.imaging.formats.tiff.constants.TiffConstants
public final class TiffConstants extends Object
Defines constants for internal elements from TIFF files and for allowing applications to define parameters for reading and writing TIFF files.

    • TIFF_LZW_COMPRESSION_BLOCK_SIZE_MEDIUM

      public static final int TIFF_LZW_COMPRESSION_BLOCK_SIZE_MEDIUM
      Specifies a larger strip-size to be used for compression. This setting generally produces smaller output files, but requires a slightly longer processing time. Used in conjunction with the PARAM_KEY_LZW_COMPRESSION_STRIP_SIZE
